 of your brand during a transaction."}],["$","p",null,{"children":["In 2026, where the average professional receives over ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"120 emails per day"}],", your billing email needs to do two things simultaneously: ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Stand out"}]," and ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Remove friction"}],". If a client has to search their inbox for \"that one bill from that one person,\" you have already delayed your own payment. This guide explores the etiquette and technical precision required to send emails that get your money into your bank account."]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"space-y-8","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-outfit border-b-4 border-blue-500 pb-2 inline-block","children":"The \"Subject Line\" Science"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg","children":"Your subject line is the most important factor in how fast you get paid. It must be searchable for the client's accounting department."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"p-8 bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-100 rounded-[2.5rem]","children":[["$","h5",null,{"className":"font-bold text-red-600 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs","children":"The \"Bad\" Way"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500 italic","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"\"Invoice\""}],["$","li",null,{"children":"\"Hey, here is the bill\""}],["$","li",null,{"children":"\"Billing for December\""}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-6 text-xs text-red-400","children":"Why? These are vague and impossible to find in a search 3 months later during audit season."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"p-8 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-100 rounded-[2.5rem]","children":[["$","h5",null,{"className":"font-bold text-green-600 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs","children":"The \"Professional\" Way"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-2 text